videos.description: Nick Starkel lobs it down field to Christian Kirk for a 60-yard touchdown to give the Aggies an early lead.
videos.headline: Texas A&M scores early with TD

videos.description: Jhamon Ausbon drags defender into end zone for a 10-yard touchdown to widen the Aggies lead over the Lobos.
videos.headline: Texas A&M pads lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Keith Ford finds a gap and rushes 10 yards into the end zone for an Aggies touchdown early in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Ford rushes into the end zone untouched for TD

videos.description: Damion Ratley juggles the ball on his way into the end zone for an Aggies touchdown to extend their lead.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Ratley makes a juggling catch for TD

videos.description: Christian Kirk turns on the jets and takes the punt return 90 yards for an Aggies touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Kirk returns punt for TD

videos.description: Nick Starkel throws it deep to Damion Ratley who fights off a defender to make his way into the end zone for a 36-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Starkel goes deep for TD

videos.description: Trayveon Williams finds a gap and easily makes his way into the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas A&M widens lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Elijah Lilly takes the kickoff  all the way to the house for an impressive 100-yard touchdown to get the Lobos on the board.
videos.headline: New Mexico's Lilly returns kickoff for 100 yard TD

videos.description: Daryl Chestnut rushes 3 yards into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: New Mexico's Chestnut stumbles into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Kellen Mond passes it to an open Camron Buckley for a 7-yard touchdown for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Mond finds Buckley for a TD
